    public class NEATGene
extends VectorGene
implements java.lang.Comparable<NEATGene>
    Base class for representations of NEAT genes. Note that the innovation ID required by NEAT is implemented with ConfigurableBase.id (which this class extends).
    Author:
    O. J. Coleman
